OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773284606
OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FIrresponsible online adverts for
OL,7,FBrazilian butt lifts (BBLs) remain
OL,8,Fwidespread, the advertising watchdog
OL,9,Fhas warned.
OL,11,FJust 11.5% of more than 900 ads for
OL,12,Fnon-surgical liquid BBLs between April
OL,13,Fand December last year adhered to the
OL,14,Frules, the Committee of Advertising
OL,15,FPractice (CAP) said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
