CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773284606
OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FCAP said it found ads using time-
OL,7,Flimited offers that risked pressuring
OL,8,Fpeople into making quick decisions
OL,9,Fabout serious medical procedures,
OL,10,Fwhile some ads made claims such as "0%
OL,11,Finfection rate" or described
OL,12,Fprocedures as "safe" without properly
OL,13,Freflecting the risks involved.
OL,15,FOther ads played on body insecurities,
OL,16,Fpromising to "boost your confidence"
OL,17,For "transform your body effortlessly".
OL,26,@rD@dOUsD@OO]tD@OOUtD@TO]xD@NOUxD@dO]yD@
OL,26,ADOUyD@eO]
