CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773284606
OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FCAP said it was "extremely rare" to
OL,7,Fsee such a high proportion of
OL,8,Fadvertisers in one area breaking the
OL,9,Frules, suggesting "deeper problems in
OL,10,Fa sector that lacks regulation".
OL,12,FFollowing the findings, CAP has
OL,13,Fcontacted clinics telling them to
OL,14,Famend or remove ads that broke the
OL,15,Frules.
OL,17,FWhile currently legal, liquid BBLs are
OL,18,Funregulated in the UK and can lead to
OL,19,Fserious complications, CAP warned,
OL,20,Fincluding infection, sepsis and
OL,21,Fembolism.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@`O]qD@SOUrD@_O]
