OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FSurgery abroad could also involve
OL,7,Fadded risks, particularly where
OL,8,Fstandards of care differed from those
OL,9,Fin the UK.
OL,11,FFor some people, the procedures have
OL,12,Fhad "devastating" consequences,
OL,13,Fincluding serious infections, long-
OL,14,Fterm health problems and in some
OL,15,Fcases, loss of life.
OL,17,FCAP compliance executive Isabel Lucas
OL,18,Fsaid it was "deeply concerning" to see
OL,19,Fso many ads for liquid BBLs continuing
OL,20,Fto break the rules.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@QO]zD@MOUzD@_O]
