OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FShe said: "We know these procedures
OL,7,Fcarry significant risks which is why
OL,8,Fit's so important ads are responsible.
OL,10,F"Ultimately, choosing to undergo one
OL,11,Fof these procedures is a serious
OL,12,Fdecision and people deserve the space
OL,13,Fand time to make their choices in a
OL,14,Ffully informed way."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUvD@TO]
