OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773284606
OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FKerry Nicol, external affairs manager
OL,7,Fat the Chartered Trading Standards
OL,8,FInstitute (CTSI), said: "We welcome
OL,9,Fthe action taken by CAP and the
OL,10,FAdvertising Standards Authority to
OL,11,Fcrack down on irresponsible online ads
OL,12,Ffor non-surgical liquid BBLs.
OL,14,F"The scale of harm caused by the lack
OL,15,Fof regulation in the aesthetics
OL,16,Findustry is deeply alarming. Consumers
OL,17,Fare being put at risk every day by
OL,18,Funqualified practitioners preying on
OL,19,Fpeople's vulnerabilities around body
OL,20,Fimage.
OL,26,@pD@YOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
