OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773284606
OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,F"Urgent, coordinated Government and
OL,7,Fmultiagency action is needed to stop
OL,8,Fbad actors in this sector. A logical
OL,9,Fand immediate first step is the
OL,10,Fintroduction of a national licensing
OL,11,Fscheme, giving the public a clear
OL,12,Findication of who is qualified to
OL,13,Fcarry out these procedures. It's time
OL,14,Fthe UK takes public safety seriously
OL,15,Fand weed out those putting lives at
OL,16,Frisk."
OL,18,FLast month, MPs said the Government
OL,19,Fshould immediately ban BBLs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@FO]
