OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773284606
OL,3,CIrresponsible ads for Brazilian butt
OL,4,Clifts remain widespread, watchdog warns
OL,6,FThe Women and Equalities Committee
OL,7,F(WEC) of MPs accused ministers of "not
OL,8,Fmoving quickly enough" in introducing
OL,9,Fa licensing system for non-surgical
OL,10,Fcosmetic procedures.
OL,12,FA lack of regulation in the cosmetics
OL,13,Findustry had led to a "wild west"
OL,14,Fwhere patients were receiving
OL,15,Fprocedures in garden sheds, hotel
OL,16,Frooms and public toilets, they warned.
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@VO]uD@WOUuD@aO]
